title: COVID19 ICD10PCS Value Set for Administration of Tocilizumab
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to administration of tocilizumab.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes introduction of tocilizumab into central or peripheral veins via open or percutaneous routes.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes administration of other interleukin-6 antagonists (e.g., sarilumab) and routes of administration that do not involve open or percutaneous procedures (i.e. oral administration).)
